2011-06-28T12:34:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-28/european-stocks-climb-banks-mining-companies-lead-advance-in-stoxx-600.html
European stocks advanced as mining
companies and banks gained. The Stoxx Europe 600 Index increased
0.5 percent to 265.4 at 1:33 p.m. in  London , having earlier lost
as much as 0.2 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
